name: Shinjarium
description: What is Shinjarium(SJM)? Shinjarium is a cryptocurrency project that was built on Ethereum Network at the end of 2022. Shinjarium is supported by its community of enthusiasts. Shinjarium's main feature is transparency, with which will create long-term relationships and synergistic alliances within the community. Currently, Shinjarium has available its Liquidity and Token staking features. Investors simply have to pair Shinjarium tokens with ETH through Uniswap to receive LP tokens while they can stake Shinjarium tokens to earn SJM. Last but not least, Shinjarium aims to be one of the main decentralized ecosystems in the world of meme coins.
